      "raw_text": "WALLA WALLA, Wash. July 4.\nLeaders of the !, w. w. are busy\nhere today enlisting farm laborers\nin the organization for the purpose\nof securing higher wages during the\nharvets season.\n\n\nChief of Police Davis, fearful of\ntrouble such as Spokane expert\nenced, has issued orders to arrest\nanyone who attempts to 'incite a\nriot\"\n\n\n1t is estimated that 800 members\nof the organization are in Walla\nWalla.\n\n\nTwo street speakers were ar\nrested yesterday and fined heavily.\nLeaders of the Industrialists de.\nclare that they will not countenance\nany disturbances unless the police\ninterfere with street meetings."
